{
  "stem": "13817.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "When he came, we naturally were gone.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "My brother was hiding in a farm, which was outside of a town laying by itself.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The owner was a good friend of ours.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And he naturally right away took him in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I went to my grandpa's house, because he was way over 60 at that time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "He was in his-- close to 80, actually.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I saw they were safe there, but then all of a sudden the Gestapo came looking for my brother there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And they went through the whole house looking all over.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I was laying in a-- in a-- not-being-used bedroom under the bed way in the corner.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And they didn't-- they didn't see me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Then after they left, I, I got a little bit scared and went to the next town, which, which was called Duren, which was, a bit further on, a bigger city where an aunt and a-- lived with her daughter.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "The other daughter was already in Israel at that time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "It was called Palestine at that time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "She went in a youth transport.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And her husband, who was a traveling salesman, an international salesman, just happened to be at that time in Belgium, who naturally didn't come back when, when, when he heard about these things.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I thought I was safe there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In fact, I went into the streetcar after that-- I took the train.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I ran into the streetcar there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was my cousin sitting there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I gave her right away a sign not to recognize me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "How did you do that?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What was the sign?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I looked at her and shook my head.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So she right away caught on.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
